id":107540,"like":10,"dislike":25,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eAgWlPcofFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeAgWlPcofFg&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28XvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=44297db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eAgWlPcofFg</a><br />\n雖然係支那人<br />\n但分析得幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:52:23.000Z","msg":"我岩岩都見巴哈有人提呢條片<br />\n正想出個文本版俾啲唔想睇支那人片既人睇下 (雖然佢分析得幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"條女越講越嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:05:40.000Z","msg":"係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見Comment啲支那人話佢平時啲片成日笑<br />\n但係呢條就好嬲好嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e5e39fb9193be4d353a43156761c3ea161318d","tid":2329252,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"冇3080學咩人打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3473ff06f88cbaf4a812db7c43b6b3a812cbae","tid":2329252,"uid":107540,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00e5e39fb9193be4d353a43156761c3ea161318d","tid":2329252,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"冇3080學咩人打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n有30系顯卡嘅人有幾多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遊戲主要市場主機佔好大部分"},{"pid":"530bfedcf8d4b635b769879578cab0e492f26b4c","tid":2329252,"uid":159183,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:48:34.000Z","msg":"1.令人驚豔的 AI 系統，包括警察、NPC 和敵人<br />\n這其實也是原訂於今年《電馭叛客2077》宣布在 4 月 16 日延期到 9 月的原因，那就是對於 AI 的不滿意。甚至在最初訪談中，CDPR 還表示遊戲中的 AI 會讓每一位 NPC 都充滿活力，擁有獨特的行動和動畫，但結果...我們也全都知道，每一位 NPC 反應都一模一樣。<br />\n<br />\n2.完整的通緝系統和腐敗制度下的警察<br />\n原本遊戲中將會有一個可以賄賂腐敗警察的系統，甚至當你惹惱某些勢力或是傭兵公司時（遊戲設定裡的警察就是受到僱用的私人傭兵），他們還會在特定的地區追殺你；假如玩家殺掉的 NPC 太多，路人也會開始對玩家不友善、尖叫或是找警察來抓人丟進監獄。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.不同的地區、時間會出現不同武裝的警察介入<br />\n如同字面上，當玩家在不同的地區犯罪時，會看到不同武裝等級或服裝的警察介入，玩家會聽到不同的警察講不同的語言。當然這在遊戲開始直接被捨棄，玩家一犯罪就是超時空戰警出現，各種武裝直接傳送過來。<br />\n<br />\n4.更加有趣的戰鬥和駭客玩法<br />\n可以從影片中看到，以前駭客的玩法更加多樣，可以從倒地的敵人腦中獲取周圍敵人的資訊"},{"pid":"4f2edd68eac5bfe3b6df1cdea134ee02037bc297","tid":2329252,"uid":60868,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:53:02.000Z","msg":"機廢賴隻game, 你睇有人好撚enjoy隻game架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fpXqTyM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfpXqTyM.jpg&h=c0e92982&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0221cb0051a65db16692d14d832c4654443a0219","tid":2329252,"uid":61564,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9e96201ebc28c7aa5b686a5dc0e45cd3006ccd8c","tid":2329252,"uid":107540,"like":10,"dislike":25,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T06:07:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/eAgWlPcofFg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FeAgWlPcofFg&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28XvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=44297db1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/eAgWlPcofFg</a><br />\n雖然係支那人<br />\n但分析得幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T10:17:11.000Z","msg":"呢條片真係分析得好好, 佢剩係FOCUS係PERFORMANCE, 都唔太追究返出GAME前講左會出既野"},{"pid":"6c71dedb7d52b83428154448e40a1e5cc33118cf","tid":2329252,"uid":1144,"like":0,"dislike":20,"score":-20,"quote":{"pid":"2a3473ff06f88cbaf4a812db7c43b6b3a812cbae","tid":2329252,"uid":107540,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"00e5e39fb9193be4d353a43156761c3ea161318d","tid":2329252,"uid":152432,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T07:27:40.000Z","msg":"冇3080學咩人打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:45:11.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n有30系顯卡嘅人有幾多<img src=\"/as